{"tid":338899,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"到今時今日BEYOND首長城都依然係咁神","createTime":"2017-07-28T14:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T15:03:22.000Z","uid":52023,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e310eee4a9dc23c80742f1c3d76d6841039af27","tid":338899,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T14:44:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V-BBg3gP8z8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DV-BBg3gP8z8&d=leWPXQtwudMQbat4Q4cCN5Uc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=3b6c105d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V-BBg3gP8z8</a><br />\n作曲編曲都非常好就唔洗講<br />\n無論題材同歌詞都仲係食到現今社會應一應<br />\n<br />\n圍著國度,事實,歲月和理想<br />\n<br />\n香港97前唔係咁 啲人好精神 好有拼勁<br />\n唔好講有拼勁搵錢 好有拼勁養家 有拼勁生存<br />\n有人為理想博鬥 而家喺香港社會講理想<br />\n人哋會問你 理想定首期緊要？<br />\n<br />\n有幾多香港仲記得香港以前係可以自給自足<br />\n唔洗東江水 唔洗鳩鐵 唔洗乜嘢祖國懷抱國民認知都可以好地地做東方之珠<br />\n呢啲&quot;事實同真相&quot;每過一年就愈少人記得 每新一代就愈嚟愈少人知<br />\n成為香港嘅歲月 <br />\n<br />\n那裡那天不再聽到在呼號的人<br />\n<br />\n香港一路一路愈嚟愈少人嗌救命<br />\n愈嚟愈多人覺得中共惡哂係理所當然<br />\n一係投共 一係等死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e16e370ad49a5a1f9330b3dafbf82a52ea64aa4","tid":338899,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T14:46:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f585119071c981d0bacf7f5a0fe5be77213b502b","tid":338899,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:03:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}